data.description: This stunning property offers the perfect blend of space, style, and comfort. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the beautiful foyer, which creates an inviting atmosphere throughout. The heart of this home is the expansive Great room, seamlessly connected to the dining area and kitchen. This open design allows for easy flow, making it ideal for entertaining The living room features large windows that flood the space with natural light. The standout features of this home is multiple bedrooms downstairs with space upstairs for entertaining. The downstairs master bedroom offers a tranquil retreat for homeowners, complete with a spacious en-suite bathroom featuring a luxurious soaking tub, a separate shower, double vanities, and a walk-in closet. Upstairs even has a super bonus room, bedroom and full bath. The backyard oasis is a tranquil retreat with lush landscaping, a patio for outdoor dining and plenty of space for relaxation. Master Carpet and Dishwasher Allowance $1000
